            "answer": "<p>If something isn't quite right, you have 30 days to return it back to the store of purchase. Please return items in original condition and with all tags still attached. We understand circumstances can change, if you change your mind after an in-store purchase, we can offer a full credit note or exchange of an equivalent item.</p>"
